    NWCA 2011 Vascular Plant Taxa List

    taxaNWCA.Rd

    A dataset containing taxonomy and basic characteristics for vascular plant taxa as used in NWCA 2011.

    taxaNWCA

    Format

    A data frame with 3814 observations on the following 12 variables.

    SPECIES_NAME_ID

    A numeric vector containing the NWCA taxonomic ID number

    USDA_NAME

    Accepted USDA PLANTS name, or the official NWCA name where not available

    DIVISION

    Division level of taxonomy

    ORDER

    Order level of taxonomy

    FAMILY

    Family level of taxonomy

    GENUS

    Genus level of taxonomy

    SPECIES

    Species level of taxonomy

    SUBSPECIES

    Subspecies level of taxonomy

    VARIETY

    Variety level of taxonomy

    CATEGORY

    Plant category of taxon, including MONOCOT, GYMNOSPERM, DICOT, FERN, LICHEN, HORSETAIL, MOSS, LYCOPOD, and LIVERWORT

    GROWTH_HABIT

    Growth habit of taxon

    DURATION

    Lifecycle duration of taxon

    @note This dataset is the taxa list used for state-specific CC and native status values used in NWCA 2011.

    Examples

    head(taxaNWCA)
#>   SPECIES_NAME_ID                        USDA_NAME      DIVISION     ORDER
#> 1              58             xELYHORDEUM MACOUNII MAGNOLIOPHYTA CYPERALES
#> 2             135                   ABIES BALSAMEA CONIFEROPHYTA   PINALES
#> 3             142                   ABIES CONCOLOR CONIFEROPHYTA   PINALES
#> 4             146                    ABIES GRANDIS CONIFEROPHYTA   PINALES
#> 5             153                 ABIES LASIOCARPA CONIFEROPHYTA   PINALES
#> 6             155 ABIES LASIOCARPA VAR. LASIOCARPA CONIFEROPHYTA   PINALES
#>     FAMILY      GENUS    SPECIES SUBSPECIES    VARIETY   CATEGORY GROWTH_HABIT
#> 1  POACEAE ELYHORDEUM   MACOUNII                          MONOCOT    GRAMINOID
#> 2 PINACEAE      ABIES   BALSAMEA                       GYMNOSPERM         TREE
#> 3 PINACEAE      ABIES   CONCOLOR                       GYMNOSPERM         TREE
#> 4 PINACEAE      ABIES    GRANDIS                       GYMNOSPERM         TREE
#> 5 PINACEAE      ABIES LASIOCARPA                       GYMNOSPERM         TREE
#> 6 PINACEAE      ABIES LASIOCARPA            LASIOCARPA GYMNOSPERM         TREE
#>    DURATION
#> 1 PERENNIAL
#> 2 PERENNIAL
#> 3 PERENNIAL
#> 4 PERENNIAL
#> 5 PERENNIAL
#> 6 PERENNIAL
